        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> I never used to give weapons to my pet.  I found it hard enough to KS my 39 pet while soloing.  Now that KS is no longer a problem, should I be giving my pet weapons?</P><P>I'm currently lvl 47 using the 44 pet.  I'm not really sure what advantage giving my pet a weapon has other than making it look cool.  I understand that the benefit is a fixed reduction in attack delay, and any proc the weapon has.  I also believe that at lower levels, two weapons were required for the pet to dual wield. I don't intend to give a pet a weapon that procs.</P><P>Any information?  What does giving one weapon to my pet do? Two weapons?  Any changes with higher level pets, like 49?</P><P>I would appreciate any help, can't separate the facts from the myths.</P><P>Waldina<BR>Cazic-Thule Necromancer</font></td>

